Rupert's questions.

02:40.577 --> 02:42.178
Now we're gonna have to rewind.

02:42.212 --> 02:44.814
We just missed the scene where
half the team steals a tank

02:44.848 --> 02:47.050
while the other half pretends
to be a DJ for some reason.

02:47.083 --> 02:48.385
Damn it.
Yeah, okay.

02:48.418 --> 02:50.220
I'm going to the bar.
Suit yourself.

02:50.254 --> 02:53.156
Rupert and I
are just fine without you.
(door closes)

02:53.189 --> 02:54.658
(laughs) You're right.

02:54.691 --> 02:56.092
I bet he is on his period.

02:56.125 --> 02:57.827
Whatever that means.

02:57.861 --> 02:59.229
La, la, la, la.
Stop, stop, stop, stop.

02:59.263 --> 03:00.530
Gross, gross, gross.
Ew, ew, ew.

03:00.564 --> 03:02.699
No, no, no. No. Ew. Ew.

03:02.732 --> 03:04.768
A loaf of bread,
a container of milk

03:04.801 --> 03:06.770
and a stick of butter.

03:06.803 --> 03:09.105
A loaf of milk,
a container of bread

03:09.138 --> 03:11.275
and a Joe Dirt DVD.

03:11.308 --> 03:13.877
