Scarlett Johansson

03:13.910 --> 03:16.112
and treasure from a fish tank.

03:18.582 --> 03:20.083
P.A. ANNOUNCER:
Attention, shoppers.

03:20.116 --> 03:22.352
Beloved cereal icon Boo Berry

03:22.386 --> 03:24.888
is now greeting customers
in aisle six.

03:24.921 --> 03:26.623
(gasps) Boo Berry?

03:26.656 --> 03:28.191
The Boo Berry?

03:28.224 --> 03:30.059
Are there imposter Boo Berries?

03:30.093 --> 03:31.561
Hey, watch it.

03:31.595 --> 03:34.531
Oh, Mr. Boo Berry,
I'm your biggest fan.

03:34.564 --> 03:36.132
You're not the one
threatening me

03:36.165 --> 03:37.267
on Facebook, are you?

03:37.301 --> 03:40.304
No, no. No, not-not you.
Not you.

03:40.337 --> 03:42.372
Hey, you know what I always
loved about your cereal?

03:42.406 --> 03:44.274
It tasted like blueberries.

03:44.308 --> 03:46.075
Oh, my God. Boo Berries.

03:46.109 --> 03:47.477
And you're... and
you're a ghost.

03:47.511 --> 03:49.112
'Cause... So
that-that's the "boo."

03:49.145 --> 03:51.715
Did you guys know you were
doing that? Oh, my God.

03:51.748 --> 03:54.050
Anyway, can I shake your hand?
Sure.

03:54.083 --> 03:56.085
♪

04:09.433 --> 04:10.667
(gasps)

04:10.700 --> 04:13.069
I've been touched by greatness.

04:13.102 --> 04:15.739
I am never washing
this hand again.

04:15.772 --> 04:17.441
This is the best thing
to happen to me

04:17.474 --> 04:19.008
since I became a wisecracking,

04:19.042 --> 04:21.445
fourth-wall-breaking superhero.

04:21.478 --> 04:22.912
Call me Redstool.

04:22.946 --> 04:24.247
The treatment
didn't give me powers,

04:24.280 --> 04:26.350
but it did spread cancer
to my anus.

04:26.383 --> 04:28.418
♪ Just call me anus ♪

04:28.452 --> 04:30.286
♪ Of the morning ♪

04:30.320 --> 04:31.688
♪ Anus ♪

04:31.721 --> 04:34.358
♪ Just touch my cheek ♪

04:34.391 --> 04:36.259
♪ Before you leave me ♪

04:36.292 --> 04:38.962
♪ Anus ♪

04:38.995 --> 04:42.832
♪ This violence
juxtaposed to music ♪

04:42.866 --> 04:44.834
♪ Anus ♪

04:44.868 --> 04:47.437
♪ Decapitation ♪

04:47.471 --> 04:49.673
♪ In slow-motion ♪

04:49.706 --> 04:52.476
♪ Anus. ♪

04:55.311 --> 04:57.046
(action music plays on TV)

04:59.649 --> 05:01.951
(yawns)

05:01.985 --> 05:03.987
Sorry, Rupert.
I think I'm down for the count.

05:04.020 --> 05:05.522
You okay if I go to bed?

05:05.555 --> 05:06.823
Oh, I like
that we're comfortable

05:06.856 --> 05:08.024
doing things separately, too.

05:08.057 --> 05:09.826
Good night.

05:09.859 --> 05:12.195
Do me a favor and don't wake me
when you come up, though.

05:12.228 --> 05:14.831
Yes, you do. You always step
on the creaky board.

05:14.864 --> 05:17.133
Yes, you do. Every time.

05:17.166 --> 05:19.503
No, you' being a little bitch.

05:20.604 --> 05:21.671
