05:28.512 --> 05:30.380
Now you say you're sorry.

05:30.414 --> 05:33.049
What do you mean, "For what"?
I hate you!

05:34.350 --> 05:35.652
(groans)

05:35.685 --> 05:36.920
I'm sorry. I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

05:36.953 --> 05:38.755
I love you. I value you.

05:38.788 --> 05:40.490
