06:56.032 --> 06:57.233
Murderer!

06:57.266 --> 06:59.068
You killed Rupert.

06:59.102 --> 07:00.403
Whoa, whoa, whoa,
whoa, whoa, whoa.

07:00.436 --> 07:01.838
Hey, whoa.
Hey, what's going on?

07:01.871 --> 07:04.908
You killed my best friend
is what's going on.

07:04.941 --> 07:06.843
Oh. Uh-oh.

07:06.876 --> 07:08.277
Bear-killing bastard.

07:08.311 --> 07:10.847
Oh, my God.
Stewie, I am so sorry.

07:10.880 --> 07:12.415
I-I was drunk. It
was an accident.

07:12.448 --> 07:14.150
I must have thought
he was a chew toy.

07:14.183 --> 07:16.319
So? If you were driving drunk
and ran him over,

07:16.352 --> 07:17.754
would you still go to jail?

07:17.787 --> 07:19.155
Yes! You killed him.

07:19.188 --> 07:20.590
Let me make it up
to you, please.

07:20.624 --> 07:21.858
How about you kill
something I love?

07:21.891 --> 07:23.459
How about I do that?

07:23.493 --> 07:25.161
Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa,
whoa, whoa, whoa. Okay.

07:25.194 --> 07:27.096
Okay, that's-that's
fine. That's fair.

07:27.130 --> 07:28.698
No, I-I meant, like-like...

07:28.732 --> 07:30.166
like my favorite tennis ball.

07:30.199 --> 07:32.536
You're comparing Rupert
to a tennis ball?

07:32.569 --> 07:33.970
What is wrong with you?

07:34.003 --> 07:35.371
No wonder you two
never got along.

07:35.404 --> 07:37.541
He always knew there was
something off about you,

07:37.574 --> 07:39.709
and now we know what it was.
You're a psycho!

07:39.743 --> 07:41.177
Stewie, I didn't mean to...
Shut up!

07:41.210 --> 07:43.279
You don't understand. I...
Shut up.

07:43.312 --> 07:45.849
Stop trying. It's over.

07:45.882 --> 07:47.383
Look at me. Watch.
See what I'm doing?

07:47.416 --> 07:49.118
Twitter: unfollow.

07:49.152 --> 07:50.887
Instagram: unfollow.

07:50.920 --> 07:52.722
Snapchat: unfollow.

07:52.756 --> 07:54.791
And there we go. Done.

07:54.824 --> 07:56.492
We are not friends anymore.

07:56.526 --> 07:57.894
But, Stewie...
Bye.

07:57.927 --> 08:00.063
Dikembe Mutombo, will
you do the thing?

08:00.096 --> 08:02.532
Brian, you are blocked.

08:02.566 --> 08:04.400
(laughs)

08:06.502 --> 08:08.504
