08:11.875 --> 08:14.177
Why are you brushing your teeth
with your left hand?

08:14.210 --> 08:15.979
Can't risk the right
getting wet, Lois.

08:16.012 --> 08:17.480
Boo Berry touched it,

08:17.513 --> 08:19.916
and it is now a sacred space,
like a temple.

08:19.949 --> 08:21.885
Okay. Well, I'm gonna have
middle-aged woman,

08:21.918 --> 08:24.654
boobs-falling-off-to-the-side
sleep now.

08:24.688 --> 08:28.124
(snores)

08:32.361 --> 08:33.997
Hey, Chris, have you seen...

08:34.030 --> 08:36.099
What, uh... what-what
are you doing?

08:36.132 --> 08:39.102
Operating my thriving
quinceañera dress business.

08:39.135 --> 08:40.904
Do me a favor,
stand on that chair?

08:40.937 --> 08:43.372
Uh, okay.

08:43.406 --> 08:45.108
So, what's up?

08:45.141 --> 08:46.910
I'm looking for Stewie.
He and I had a fight,

08:46.943 --> 08:48.778
and I'm scared he might've
done something drastic.

08:48.812 --> 08:50.046
Him? (chuckles)

08:50.079 --> 08:51.615
You're the one
who killed his friend.

08:51.648 --> 08:54.117
Okay, I see he got
to you before I did.

08:54.150 --> 08:55.852
It's a stuffed animal, Chris.

08:55.885 --> 08:58.187
Yeah, well, he cremated
that stuffed animal,

08:58.221 --> 09:01.057
and he's going to Vermont
to scatter the ashes.

09:01.090 --> 09:02.759
What? I got to go after him.

09:02.792 --> 09:04.761
Not until I finish fitting this.

09:04.794 --> 09:06.596
How you feeling?
Bueno? Fits good?

09:06.630 --> 09:07.864
This isn't mine.

09:07.897 --> 09:11.234
Do you or do you not
feel bonita?

09:11.267 --> 09:12.468
I feel bonita.

09:12.501 --> 09:15.138
Wonderful,
because you look bonita.

09:15.171 --> 09:19.008
Gracias, cariña,
puedes recogerlo el miércoles.

09:20.109 --> 09:24.280
Pablo is gonna lose his mind.

09:24.313 --> 09:26.082
Mwah.

09:30.654 --> 09:31.821
Stewie!

09:31.855 --> 09:33.723
Hmm. Well, violent murderers

09:33.757 --> 09:35.258
can often be found
at bus stations,

09:35.291 --> 09:36.459
so why am I surprised?

09:36.492 --> 09:38.127
You can't go to Vermont alone.

09:38.161 --> 09:39.729
I'm not. Got Rupert with me.

09:39.763 --> 09:41.430
He and I had an agreement:

09:41.464 --> 09:44.300
