scatter his ashes on a mountain.

09:44.333 --> 09:46.670
If I died first,
he would throw my body whole

09:46.703 --> 09:48.437
into the fountain
at the Bellagio.

09:48.471 --> 09:49.806
I don't care.
I'm coming with you.

09:49.839 --> 09:51.240
Well, you're not
going to sit with me.

09:51.274 --> 09:52.842
Oh, come on.
If I don't, I'll get stuck

09:52.876 --> 09:54.744
next to that guy
with the heavy hands.

09:54.778 --> 09:56.245
Hi, doggy.

09:56.279 --> 09:57.480
(groans)

09:57.513 --> 09:59.082
(chuckles) Serves you right.

09:59.115 --> 10:00.149
And a baby.

10:00.183 --> 10:02.485
(groans)

10:02.518 --> 10:04.453
(bird squawking)

10:15.231 --> 10:17.233
♪

10:28.544 --> 10:30.479
