step further,

10:33.717 --> 10:35.251
or I will hit you.

10:36.585 --> 10:37.486
That's it!

10:37.520 --> 10:38.654
(grunts)

10:38.688 --> 10:41.057
Leave! Me! Alone! Murderer!

10:41.090 --> 10:42.658
Stewie, stop!
Stop, all right?

10:42.692 --> 10:45.361
Look, why are you being
such a jerk over a stupid bear?

10:45.394 --> 10:47.196
Don't you disrespect
the dead!

10:47.230 --> 10:48.865
♪

10:48.898 --> 10:50.366
(growls)

10:52.736 --> 10:53.703
Aah!

10:53.737 --> 10:56.172
(grunting)

10:56.205 --> 10:57.540
Aah!

10:58.942 --> 11:00.877
He's not dead!
He was never alive!

11:00.910 --> 11:02.045
You take those words back!

11:02.078 --> 11:03.346
He wouldn't care!

11:03.379 --> 11:04.814
He didn't hear them!
He's a doll!

11:04.848 --> 11:07.483
He was my best friend!

11:07.516 --> 11:09.018
I'm supposed to be
your best friend.

11:09.052 --> 11:10.586
Well, you're not!

11:10.619 --> 11:13.056
You're a bloodthirsty,
cold-hearted murderer!

11:13.089 --> 11:14.490
Fine. You're right.

11:14.523 --> 11:16.025
You know what?
It wasn't an accident.

11:16.059 --> 11:17.560
I knew he wasn't a chew toy.

11:17.593 --> 11:19.495
I was sick of you talking
to him all the time.

11:19.528 --> 11:21.097
I was sick of you complaining
to him about me

11:21.130 --> 11:22.866
when I'm right there
in the room.

11:22.899 --> 11:25.835
And I was sick of always playing
second fiddle to that bear!

11:25.869 --> 11:28.237
He's not even real!

11:28.271 --> 11:30.239
You did it...

11:30.273 --> 11:32.375
