11:45.421 --> 11:47.023
(grunts, straining)

11:47.056 --> 11:49.225
Oh, my God, Stewie!

11:49.258 --> 11:50.693
(imitates bomb exploding)

11:50.726 --> 11:53.296
Ah, I didn't know we
were blowing it up.

11:55.765 --> 11:57.767
