12:03.406 --> 12:05.074
Rupert! Where...

12:05.108 --> 12:06.742
Oh, there you are.

12:06.776 --> 12:08.477
Stewie, you're hurt.
It's just my ankle.

12:08.511 --> 12:10.814
It's not a big deal.
It's already swelling up.

12:10.847 --> 12:12.381
Just let me...
Back off!

12:12.415 --> 12:14.417
I'm doing this on my own.
For Rupert.

12:14.450 --> 12:16.452
(grunting)

12:17.787 --> 12:19.755
(sighs) Damn it,
Stewie, just...

12:19.789 --> 12:21.424
just sit there, will ya?

12:21.457 --> 12:23.359
I'll-I'll get us up.

12:24.627 --> 12:25.829
I didn't want your help.

12:25.862 --> 12:27.463
Well, you need it,
so it's happening.

12:30.333 --> 12:33.136
