forgive you, you know.

12:33.169 --> 12:35.771
That's fine.
I'm going to say
uncomplimentary things

12:35.805 --> 12:38.574
about your ass
the whole way.
Go ahead.

12:38.607 --> 12:41.177
You know, maybe it's appropriate
that you're my ride up.

12:41.210 --> 12:43.412
