my "bitch."

12:43.446 --> 12:45.348
Want to know some
of the other things
he called you?

12:45.381 --> 12:46.749
Fat Lassie.

12:46.782 --> 12:48.084
Scooby-Don't.

12:48.117 --> 12:49.452
Rin Tin Twink.

12:49.485 --> 12:50.686
Poopy Snoopy.

12:50.719 --> 12:52.321
Marma-dookie.

12:52.355 --> 12:54.991
Clifford the Big Red Sphincter
