♪ How do I ♪

18:33.529 --> 18:36.432
♪ Say good-bye ♪

18:36.465 --> 18:41.170
♪ To what we had? ♪

18:41.204 --> 18:43.372
♪ The good times ♪

18:43.406 --> 18:46.041
♪ That made us laugh ♪

18:46.074 --> 18:49.678
♪ Outweigh the bad ♪

18:51.680 --> 18:54.116
♪ I thought ♪

18:54.149 --> 18:57.853
♪ We'd get to see
forever ♪

18:57.886 --> 19:00.723
♪ But forever's ♪

19:00.756 --> 19:04.159
♪ Gone away ♪

19:04.193 --> 19:06.995
(harmonizing):
♪ It's so hard ♪

19:07.029 --> 19:10.533
♪ To say good-bye ♪

19:10.566 --> 19:13.636
♪ To yesterday ♪
(raises pitch):
♪ To yesterday... ♪

19:13.669 --> 19:15.471
♪ Go up there, Brian. ♪

19:15.504 --> 19:17.906
Okay, Brian,
now pour it out.

19:17.940 --> 19:19.708
What?
Pour it out,
whatever you have.

19:19.742 --> 19:21.244
Pour it out.

19:21.277 --> 19:23.479
I have a Gatorade bottle
full of pee from the bus.

19:23.512 --> 19:26.215
Pour it out for Rupert.

19:29.017 --> 19:31.019
♪

